<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>You can't even take a breath</i>
<i>in the sleepless city</i></b></font>

13
00:00:44,084 --> 00:00:48,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Never showing weakness but laughing</i></b></font>

14
