<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Safety is in lies, truth is empty</i></b></font>

15
00:00:52,164 --> 00:00:56,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>On the edge of danger,</i>
<i>I wanna shout and break out!</i></b></font>

16
