<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Now we gotta start let's get move!!</i></b></font>

17
00:00:57,934 --> 00:00:59,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Let's move into the brand new world</i></b></font>

18
00:00:59,834 --> 00:01:02,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Let's dive into the brand new trip</i></b></font>

19
00:01:02,074 --> 00:01:05,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Frightened by the wide world</i></b></font>

20
00:01:05,844 --> 00:01:10,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>We've just begun, now we go</i>
<i>full speed and funky beat</i></b></font>

21
00:01:10,114 --> 00:01:13,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>We will shine around the world</i></b></font>

22
00:01:13,514 --> 00:01:16,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Trip to the world</i>
<i>Yo! Here we go unknown world</i></b></font>

23
00:01:16,284 --> 00:01:18,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>We newborn travelers</i></b></font>

24
00:01:18,354 --> 00:01:20,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The unfamiliar walk is still charming</i></b></font>

25
00:01:20,554 --> 00:01:22,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The place you want to go is under your feet!</i></b></font>

26
00:01:22,424 --> 00:01:23,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>So many people in this world</i></b></font>

27
00:01:23,764 --> 00:01:26,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>It's not as if there isn't</i>
<i>backstabbing once in a while</i></b></font>

28
00:01:26,194 --> 00:01:28,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Let's warp past these boring things</i></b></font>

29
00:01:28,034 --> 00:01:29,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>And go straight to our reason for living</i></b></font>

30
00:01:29,534 --> 00:01:31,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>That's our law!</i></b></font>

31
00:03:04,994 --> 00:03:07,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He hasn't changed a bit.</b></font>

32
00:03:10,204 --> 00:03:16,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Act 1: The Ultimate Tofu Store Drift"</b></font>

33
00:03:18,044 --> 00:03:21,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Even the 1991 model costs 1.3 million yen.</b></font>

34
00:03:21,844 --> 00:03:25,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The S13 is expensive.</b></font>

35
00:03:25,944 --> 00:03:27,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Like I thought, it's gotta be the Eight-Six.</b></font>

36
00:03:27,684 --> 00:03:29,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The Eight-Six is a real possibility.</b></font>

37
00:03:29,414 --> 00:03:33,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Anyway, the car has to be FR. Right, Takumi?</b></font>

38
00:03:33,054 --> 00:03:35,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi!</b></font>

39
00:03:35,124 --> 00:03:37,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey! Are you listening?</b></font>

40
00:03:37,364 --> 00:03:39,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm listening, Itsuki.</b></font>

41
00:03:39,264 --> 00:03:42,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So how much is this Eight-Six?</b></font>

42
00:03:42,594 --> 00:03:44,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Well, this one is 300,000 yen...</b></font>

43
00:03:44,704 --> 00:03:46,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...but it hasn't passed inspection.</b></font>

44
00:03:46,364 --> 00:03:48,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>How much have you saved so far?</b></font>

45
00:03:48,604 --> 00:03:50,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>About 50,000 yen.</b></font>

46
00:03:50,704 --> 00:03:52,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You've got a long way to go.</b></font>

47
00:03:52,474 --> 00:03:54,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah... Yeah...</b></font>

48
00:03:56,374 --> 00:03:59,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Isn't there any way to make
a lot of quick money?!</b></font>

49
00:03:59,914 --> 00:04:01,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>With our current part-time
jobs at the gas station,</b></font>

50
00:04:01,484 --> 00:04:03,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>even if we work full-time
during summer break,</b></font>

51
00:04:03,054 --> 00:04:05,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>we'll only make 120,000 yen at most.</b></font>

52
00:04:05,054 --> 00:04:08,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There's gotta be a better job out there.</b></font>

53
00:04:08,194 --> 00:04:11,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You guys are working part-time?</b></font>

54
00:04:11,224 --> 00:04:12,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Mogi...?</b></font>

55
00:04:17,764 --> 00:04:21,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What? Is it so strange that I'm talking to you?</b></font>

56
00:04:21,734 --> 00:04:23,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Not really...</b></font>

57
00:04:23,504 --> 00:04:26,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You said you could get 120,000
working full-time this summer.</b></font>

58
00:04:26,004 --> 00:04:28,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>How many hours are you
supposed to work every day?</b></font>

59
00:04:28,444 --> 00:04:30,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>From early in the morning till late at night.</b></font>

60
00:04:30,384 --> 00:04:31,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What?!</b></font>

61
00:04:31,784 --> 00:04:35,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You can only make 120,000
a month for that much work?!</b></font>

62
00:04:35,454 --> 00:04:37,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's about right...</b></font>

63
00:04:37,184 --> 00:04:41,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Wages for high school students are really low!</b></font>

64
00:04:41,424 --> 00:04:43,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I didn't know...</b></font>

65
00:04:43,294 --> 00:04:46,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I've never had a part-time job...</b></font>

66
00:04:50,194 --> 00:04:52,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Good luck with your job!</b></font>

67
00:04:52,034 --> 00:04:54,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Let's get together after finals!</b></font>

68
00:04:54,804 --> 00:04:57,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Sure!</b></font>

69
00:04:57,644 --> 00:05:00,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>She just said, "Let's get together!" didn't she?</b></font>

70
00:05:00,544 --> 00:05:04,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Yeah.
--Go out with Mogi?!</b></font>

71
00:05:04,014 --> 00:05:06,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Good! Good!</b></font>

72
00:05:06,414 --> 00:05:08,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi, why didn't you tell me?</b></font>

73
00:05:08,484 --> 00:05:14,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--You should have told me you're Mogi's friend.
--I haven't talked with her in about a year.</b></font>

74
00:05:14,494 --> 00:05:17,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We were in the same club.</b></font>

75
00:05:17,024 --> 00:05:19,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We talked a lot until last summer.</b></font>

76
00:05:19,994 --> 00:05:23,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What are you talking about?
Who cares about that?</b></font>

77
00:05:23,704 --> 00:05:27,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Natsuki Mogi...! What a great turn of events!</b></font>

78
00:05:27,204 --> 00:05:30,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I've been checking her out
for a while... She's so cute...</b></font>

79
00:05:37,114 --> 00:05:40,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi! Hey, Takumi! Quit zoning out!</b></font>

80
00:05:40,284 --> 00:05:42,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If we don't hurry, we'll be in big trouble!</b></font>

81
00:05:42,014 --> 00:05:43,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We've got a grammar test next class!</b></font>

82
00:05:43,684 --> 00:05:45,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Wait up!</b></font>

83
00:05:47,794 --> 00:05:51,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, why don't we buy an Eight-Six together?!</b></font>

84
00:05:51,564 --> 00:05:54,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If we combine our money,
we can afford the loan.</b></font>

85
00:05:54,194 --> 00:05:55,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No way.</b></font>

86
00:05:55,364 --> 00:05:58,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Why do you want a car that badly?</b></font>

87
00:05:58,204 --> 00:06:00,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Your family already has a car, right?</b></font>

88
00:06:00,604 --> 00:06:02,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's no good.</b></font>

89
00:06:02,004 --> 00:06:05,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>My old man's car is an automatic
and front-wheel drive.</b></font>

90
00:06:05,704 --> 00:06:09,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>And it's a diesel. It's crap.</b></font>

91
00:06:09,514 --> 00:06:11,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I wouldn't even call it a car...</b></font>

92
00:06:13,344 --> 00:06:16,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It has four tires and it runs. It's a car.</b></font>

93
00:06:16,914 --> 00:06:18,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You just don't get it.</b></font>

94
00:06:18,884 --> 00:06:22,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If it's not fun on the mountain pass,
you can't call it a car.</b></font>

95
00:06:22,824 --> 00:06:24,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What do you do on the mountain?</b></font>

96
00:06:24,924 --> 00:06:28,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What do you think?! We're going
to challenge the corners!</b></font>

97
00:06:28,694 --> 00:06:30,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Challenge the corners...?</b></font>

98
00:06:30,504 --> 00:06:32,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Is that fun?</b></font>

99
00:06:32,934 --> 00:06:34,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Of course it's fun!</b></font>

100
00:06:34,904 --> 00:06:39,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're a guy and you don't
want to tackle the corners?!</b></font>

101
00:06:39,874 --> 00:06:43,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm already tired of that kind of stuff.</b></font>

102
00:06:43,174 --> 00:06:45,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What? What do you mean?</b></font>

103
00:06:45,414 --> 00:06:48,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We just got our licenses last month.</b></font>

104
00:07:05,664 --> 00:07:06,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You look cute.</b></font>

105
00:07:06,734 --> 00:07:10,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That outfit always looks great on you.</b></font>

106
00:07:10,034 --> 00:07:12,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Really? Thank you, Papa.</b></font>

107
00:07:15,174 --> 00:07:20,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You know, Papa, one of my
classmates is working part-time.</b></font>

108
00:07:20,914 --> 00:07:25,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He says even if he works all summer,</b></font>

109
00:07:25,884 --> 00:07:28,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>he'll only earn 120,000 yen.</b></font>

110
00:07:28,724 --> 00:07:31,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Well, that's about right.</b></font>

111
00:07:31,394 --> 00:07:35,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's hard earning money, isn't it?</b></font>

112
00:07:35,994 --> 00:07:42,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You spend more than that on me in a month.</b></font>

113
00:07:42,004 --> 00:07:44,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Is it really all right to spend so much on me?</b></font>

114
00:07:44,844 --> 00:07:49,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Of course. You're worth it.</b></font>

115
00:07:49,514 --> 00:07:51,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Really?</b></font>

116
00:07:51,284 --> 00:07:53,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't understand...</b></font>

117
00:07:57,084 --> 00:07:59,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Thank you very much!
--Thank you very much!</b></font>

118
00:07:59,554 --> 00:08:04,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, Takumi! Please think
about the Eight-Six deal.</b></font>

119
00:08:04,694 --> 00:08:07,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't care about an Eight-Six!</b></font>

120
00:08:07,534 --> 00:08:10,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You kids have good taste...</b></font>

121
00:08:10,804 --> 00:08:12,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...trying to get an Eight-Six.</b></font>

122
00:08:12,564 --> 00:08:16,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>See? See? Iketani thinks so too, right?!</b></font>

123
00:08:16,734 --> 00:08:19,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah, the Eight-Six is a good car.</b></font>

124
00:08:19,204 --> 00:08:20,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I told you.</b></font>

125
00:08:20,874 --> 00:08:22,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But I...</b></font>

126
00:08:22,244 --> 00:08:26,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>To be honest, I don't know
what an Eight-Six is.</b></font>

127
00:08:26,214 --> 00:08:28,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Who makes it?</b></font>

128
00:08:28,254 --> 00:08:30,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Are you serious, Takumi?</b></font>

129
00:08:30,154 --> 00:08:31,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Want to drink some high octane?</b></font>

130
00:08:31,984 --> 00:08:34,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Working at a gas station and
you don't know the Eight-Six?!</b></font>

131
00:08:34,654 --> 00:08:36,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What a disgrace!</b></font>

132
00:08:36,654 --> 00:08:39,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Oh, well. It's no surprise.</b></font>

133
00:08:39,494 --> 00:08:44,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>When the Nine-Two model came out,
you guys were just in 2nd or 3rd grade.</b></font>

134
00:08:44,034 --> 00:08:47,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We have an old car at my house,
but we just use it for our deliveries.</b></font>

135
00:08:47,604 --> 00:08:49,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You can't compare that to an Eight-Six!</b></font>

136
00:08:49,334 --> 00:08:52,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Even if it's old, the Eight-Six is special!</b></font>

137
00:08:52,744 --> 00:08:56,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>When we buy an Eight-Six,
will you let us join your team?</b></font>

138
00:08:56,014 --> 00:08:59,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I've always dreamed of joining
the Akina Speed Stars.</b></font>

139
00:08:59,244 --> 00:09:01,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Sure! Oh, by the way...</b></font>

140
00:09:01,014 --> 00:09:05,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's Saturday, so everyone is
meeting at Mt. Akina tonight.</b></font>

141
00:09:05,454 --> 00:09:07,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You guys wanna come along?</b></font>

142
00:09:07,054 --> 00:09:09,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What?! Can we?</b></font>

143
00:09:09,694 --> 00:09:12,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But we don't have a car...</b></font>

144
00:09:12,124 --> 00:09:14,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll give you a ride.</b></font>

145
00:09:17,634 --> 00:09:20,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We can ride in your S13?!</b></font>

146
00:09:20,304 --> 00:09:22,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll go! I'll go! I'm definitely going!</b></font>

147
00:09:22,474 --> 00:09:24,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're going too. Right, Takumi?
This is a rare opportunity!</b></font>

148
00:09:24,904 --> 00:09:29,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Um, I never said I wanted to go.
--Cool! I can meet the whole team!</b></font>

149
00:09:33,184 --> 00:09:35,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Excuse us. We're going home!</b></font>

150
00:09:35,154 --> 00:09:38,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>All right! I'll pick you up
at the bus stop at 8 PM.</b></font>

151
00:09:38,184 --> 00:09:39,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Okay!</b></font>

152
00:09:41,154 --> 00:09:43,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're really into it.
Which mountain are you going to?</b></font>

153
00:09:43,754 --> 00:09:48,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Boss, Mt. Akina is the only mountain
around here worth racing on.</b></font>

154
00:09:48,364 --> 00:09:52,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We're the fastest team on Mt. Akina.</b></font>

155
00:09:52,334 --> 00:09:56,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Many claim that they're
the fastest on Mt. Akina.</b></font>

156
00:09:56,004 --> 00:09:57,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>When I was still racing,</b></font>

157
00:09:57,844 --> 00:10:01,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>there was a guy that everyone
admitted was the fastest.</b></font>

158
00:10:01,544 --> 00:10:05,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>And he's still driving on Mt. Akina.</b></font>

159
00:10:05,344 --> 00:10:07,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Still?!</b></font>

160
00:10:07,014 --> 00:10:09,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I know all the racers at Akina...</b></font>

161
00:10:09,954 --> 00:10:12,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...but none of them are that old.</b></font>

162
00:10:12,854 --> 00:10:17,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's just because he drives during
a different time. Because...</b></font>

163
00:10:17,254 --> 00:10:19,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...he's now the owner of a tofu shop.</b></font>

164
00:10:19,764 --> 00:10:21,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What?</b></font>

165
00:10:21,864 --> 00:10:23,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>About 4 o'clock in the morning,</b></font>

166
00:10:23,864 --> 00:10:26,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>he delivers his tofu to the hotels at Lake Akina.</b></font>

167
00:10:26,364 --> 00:10:30,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's amazing to watch his downhill speed.</b></font>

168
00:10:30,304 --> 00:10:31,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Because it's his business,</b></font>

169
00:10:31,444 --> 00:10:33,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>he makes the run every day,
even in the rain and snow.</b></font>

170
00:10:33,804 --> 00:10:39,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He knows even the smallest stain
on the asphalt on Mt. Akina.</b></font>

171
00:10:39,614 --> 00:10:40,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'd even bet on it.</b></font>

172
00:10:40,914 --> 00:10:42,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The fastest downhill car on Mt. Akina...</b></font>

173
00:10:42,584 --> 00:10:44,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...is the Eight-Six from the tofu shop.</b></font>

174
00:10:44,324 --> 00:10:46,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The Eight-Six from the tofu shop?!</b></font>

175
00:10:46,324 --> 00:10:48,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Green Shopping Street"</b></font>

176
00:10:53,894 --> 00:10:56,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Going out, Takumi?</b></font>

177
00:10:56,294 --> 00:10:58,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah. I have plans with Itsuki.</b></font>

178
00:10:58,964 --> 00:11:00,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't care if you're out at night,</b></font>

179
00:11:00,504 --> 00:11:02,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but I'll drag you out of bed if you
don't wake up in the morning.</b></font>

180
00:11:02,374 --> 00:11:05,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You don't need to remind me.</b></font>

181
00:11:05,044 --> 00:11:07,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm going.</b></font>

182
00:11:23,754 --> 00:11:25,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Shut up, Takumi!</b></font>

183
00:11:25,364 --> 00:11:27,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're ruining Iketani's concentration.</b></font>

184
00:11:27,694 --> 00:11:31,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Whatever! But this sucks, and I'm scared!</b></font>

185
00:11:31,564 --> 00:11:35,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No big deal. Everyone gets scared
when they ride with a street racer.</b></font>

186
00:11:35,634 --> 00:11:38,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Next, we'll take the hairpin in second gear!</b></font>

187
00:11:45,044 --> 00:11:47,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're still too noisy, Takumi!</b></font>

188
00:11:51,054 --> 00:11:54,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>All right. Tonight, I'm going all out.</b></font>

189
00:11:57,724 --> 00:11:59,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Are you all right, Takumi?</b></font>

190
00:11:59,464 --> 00:12:01,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I didn't think you'd get that scared...</b></font>

191
00:12:01,564 --> 00:12:04,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I was in the mood and
pushed the car quite a bit.</b></font>

192
00:12:06,164 --> 00:12:09,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're a wimp, Takumi! Shame on you!</b></font>

193
00:12:09,004 --> 00:12:12,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're the type who screams
on roller coasters, aren't you?!</b></font>

194
00:12:12,504 --> 00:12:16,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I've never thought that
roller coasters are scary.</b></font>

195
00:12:16,344 --> 00:12:18,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's not like that...</b></font>

196
00:12:18,744 --> 00:12:23,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Itsuki, even if I explained it to you,
you'd never understand...</b></font>

197
00:12:23,214 --> 00:12:25,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...this fear...</b></font>

198
00:12:25,184 --> 00:12:26,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What?</b></font>

199
00:12:39,534 --> 00:12:41,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I've never seen them before...</i></b></font>

200
00:12:41,534 --> 00:12:44,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>They're headed for Mt. Akina</i>
<i>at this time of the night?</i></b></font>

201
00:12:45,644 --> 00:12:48,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Something may happen</i>
<i>on the mountain tonight.</i></b></font>

202
00:13:00,154 --> 00:13:02,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We've got visitors.</b></font>

203
00:13:13,904 --> 00:13:15,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The Red Suns?</i></b></font>

204
00:13:15,574 --> 00:13:18,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Are they the Red Suns,</i>
<i>the fastest drivers in Akagi?</i></b></font>

205
00:13:42,034 --> 00:13:46,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We're the members of
the Akagi Red Suns Team.</b></font>

206
00:13:46,364 --> 00:13:48,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't want to be rude, but...</b></font>

207
00:13:48,634 --> 00:13:53,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Who's the fastest team, or driver,
on this mountain? Please tell us.</b></font>

208
00:13:53,874 --> 00:13:56,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--What do they want?
--We're the fastest.</b></font>

209
00:13:56,144 --> 00:13:59,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We're the Akina Speed Stars Team.</b></font>

210
00:13:59,914 --> 00:14:02,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We consider ourselves the fastest here.</b></font>

211
00:14:03,514 --> 00:14:05,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Then we've found what we're looking for!</b></font>

212
00:14:05,424 --> 00:14:07,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Would you like to hold a practice session</b></font>

213
00:14:07,384 --> 00:14:10,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>with our team, the Akagi Red Suns,
here at Mt. Akina?</b></font>

214
00:14:10,224 --> 00:14:14,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--What?
--Are they serious?</b></font>

215
00:14:14,664 --> 00:14:18,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Wow! What a great turn of events!</b></font>

216
00:14:18,764 --> 00:14:20,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What do you think?</b></font>

217
00:14:20,264 --> 00:14:23,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Since we usually only run with people
we know, it's becoming routine.</b></font>

218
00:14:23,874 --> 00:14:27,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Running against other teams
gives us a new challenge.</b></font>

219
00:14:27,504 --> 00:14:30,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We can make new friends
and exchange knowledge.</b></font>

220
00:14:30,174 --> 00:14:32,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>And it improves our skills, too.</b></font>

221
00:14:32,544 --> 00:14:34,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>At first, we can run together.</b></font>

222
00:14:34,514 --> 00:14:36,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Then each team will be
represented by one driver</b></font>

223
00:14:36,254 --> 00:14:38,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>to compete in both uphill and downhill.</b></font>

224
00:14:38,084 --> 00:14:40,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We aren't concerned about winning or losing.</b></font>

225
00:14:40,024 --> 00:14:42,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We only seek to develop
friendship between the teams.</b></font>

226
00:14:42,894 --> 00:14:44,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What do you think?</b></font>

227
00:14:44,564 --> 00:14:48,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--If you put it that way, how can we refuse?
--Okay.</b></font>

228
00:14:48,594 --> 00:14:52,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>How about next Saturday at 10 o'clock?</b></font>

229
00:14:52,064 --> 00:14:53,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Okay, fine.</b></font>

230
00:14:53,764 --> 00:14:57,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Today, we'll just take it easy.</b></font>

231
00:14:57,604 --> 00:15:00,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Awesome! This is awesome, Takumi!</b></font>

232
00:15:09,154 --> 00:15:10,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We don't need to be intimidated!</b></font>

233
00:15:10,884 --> 00:15:13,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--We're going, too!
--Yeah!</b></font>

234
00:15:24,864 --> 00:15:26,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Iketani!</b></font>

235
00:15:26,734 --> 00:15:29,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Let me watch the Takahashi Brothers--</b></font>

236
00:15:29,534 --> 00:15:31,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>people call them the fastest in Akagi!</b></font>

237
00:15:31,674 --> 00:15:33,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You mean the Takahashi Brothers,</b></font>

238
00:15:33,344 --> 00:15:36,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>the famous street racers who've
been featured in the magazines?</b></font>

239
00:15:36,914 --> 00:15:40,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yes. They're also known
as "The Rotary Brothers."</b></font>

240
00:15:42,954 --> 00:15:45,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Iketani! What about us?!</b></font>

241
00:15:45,024 --> 00:15:49,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Sorry. When I make a serious run,
I don't take passengers.</b></font>

242
00:15:49,224 --> 00:15:52,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Wait here. I'll pick you up later.</b></font>

243
00:16:02,134 --> 00:16:07,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This sucks! Why're we the
only ones without a car?</b></font>

244
00:16:07,874 --> 00:16:10,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, Itsuki...</b></font>

245
00:16:10,174 --> 00:16:13,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Is it that much fun to be a street racer?</b></font>

246
00:16:14,514 --> 00:16:16,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't get it...</b></font>

247
00:16:16,314 --> 00:16:18,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Why does everyone get so excited about it?</b></font>

248
00:16:18,824 --> 00:16:21,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm the one who doesn't get it!</b></font>

249
00:16:21,054 --> 00:16:22,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We can hear the sound of cars</b></font>

250
00:16:22,524 --> 00:16:24,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>running hard one after another, right?</b></font>

251
00:16:24,254 --> 00:16:28,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Why can't you get excited about it, Takumi?!</b></font>

252
00:16:28,534 --> 00:16:30,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Excited?</b></font>

253
00:16:32,934 --> 00:16:36,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hello, Fujiwara Tofu Shop...</b></font>

254
00:16:36,004 --> 00:16:38,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Oh, it's just you.</b></font>

255
00:16:38,204 --> 00:16:40,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What a surprise...</b></font>

256
00:16:40,774 --> 00:16:41,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Just me?</b></font>

257
00:16:41,844 --> 00:16:45,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I haven't talked to you in so long,
and this is the greeting I get?</b></font>

258
00:16:46,544 --> 00:16:49,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The other day, you passed me on
your way back from a delivery.</b></font>

259
00:16:49,514 --> 00:16:52,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I signaled, but you ignored me.</b></font>

260
00:16:52,124 --> 00:16:54,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Nope, it wasn't me.</b></font>

261
00:16:54,854 --> 00:16:59,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It had to be you. It was your Eight-Six.</b></font>

262
00:16:59,024 --> 00:17:01,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Well, I mean...</b></font>

263
00:17:01,134 --> 00:17:05,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...it was my car, but I wasn't driving it.</b></font>

264
00:17:05,034 --> 00:17:08,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>My son Takumi delivers tofu to the hotels now.</b></font>

265
00:17:10,304 --> 00:17:12,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What did you say?!</b></font>

266
00:17:12,304 --> 00:17:14,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Since when?!</b></font>

267
00:17:14,144 --> 00:17:15,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Five years ago.</b></font>

268
00:17:15,874 --> 00:17:19,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Five years ago? Since he
was in the seventh grade?</b></font>

269
00:17:37,334 --> 00:17:40,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Damn! I can't keep up with them at all!</b></font>

270
00:17:45,504 --> 00:17:48,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>They're fast! I'm at my limit,</i></b></font>

271
00:17:48,044 --> 00:17:50,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>but I can't keep up with any of the Red Suns.</i></b></font>

272
00:17:58,354 --> 00:18:00,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What do you think, brother?</b></font>

273
00:18:00,684 --> 00:18:02,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They're all trash.</b></font>

274
00:18:02,224 --> 00:18:05,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Even our second string can easily beat them.</b></font>

275
00:18:05,024 --> 00:18:07,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We don't need to bring
the top drivers next week.</b></font>

276
00:18:07,394 --> 00:18:08,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll pass.</b></font>

277
00:18:08,894 --> 00:18:11,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If you're not gonna come, I guess I'll pass, too.</b></font>

278
00:18:11,704 --> 00:18:13,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No, you should run.</b></font>

279
00:18:13,504 --> 00:18:15,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You should set a record for this course</b></font>

280
00:18:15,674 --> 00:18:18,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>which the locals can never break.</b></font>

281
00:18:18,004 --> 00:18:20,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Otherwise, the name of the Akagi Red Suns</b></font>

282
00:18:20,044 --> 00:18:21,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>will never become legendary.</b></font>

283
00:18:21,814 --> 00:18:23,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah...</b></font>

284
00:18:23,574 --> 00:18:27,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>First, we'll set new records for
every course in this prefecture.</b></font>

285
00:18:27,814 --> 00:18:32,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Then we'll take Saitama,
Kanagawa, Tokyo, and Chiba.</b></font>

286
00:18:32,154 --> 00:18:34,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We'll have every record
in the entire Kanto region,</b></font>

287
00:18:34,924 --> 00:18:38,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>then we'll become legends,
and then we'll retire.</b></font>

288
00:18:38,194 --> 00:18:43,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That is the Akagi Red Suns'
"Fastest in Kanto Project."</b></font>

289
00:18:56,844 --> 00:18:58,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They're incredible.</b></font>

290
00:18:58,614 --> 00:19:01,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They are completely different from us.</b></font>

291
00:19:01,454 --> 00:19:06,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm totally shocked that we got
so beaten on our home ground.</b></font>

292
00:19:06,624 --> 00:19:10,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They've put serious money into their
suspensions, and they've got power, too.</b></font>

293
00:19:10,124 --> 00:19:12,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There's no way we can
compete with the Red Suns.</b></font>

294
00:19:12,564 --> 00:19:15,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But how can we avoid a
challenge on our own turf?</b></font>

295
00:19:15,394 --> 00:19:18,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's right! We can't back out now!</b></font>

296
00:19:18,164 --> 00:19:21,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But guts alone won't beat those guys.</b></font>

297
00:19:21,304 --> 00:19:24,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I know that... But...!</b></font>

298
00:19:24,804 --> 00:19:26,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's getting late.</b></font>

299
00:19:26,504 --> 00:19:29,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Let's get together tomorrow and talk about it.</b></font>

300
00:19:31,144 --> 00:19:33,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Street racers don't like losing.</b></font>

301
00:19:33,884 --> 00:19:37,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They get too serious about racing.</b></font>

302
00:19:37,754 --> 00:19:43,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There's nothing worse than losing to
outsiders on your own home ground.</b></font>

303
00:19:43,154 --> 00:19:47,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's like a law for street racers.</b></font>

304
00:19:56,604 --> 00:19:59,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Where's Ryosuke?</b></font>

305
00:19:59,344 --> 00:20:01,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He went home a while ago.</b></font>

306
00:20:01,074 --> 00:20:03,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We're the only ones still here.</b></font>

307
00:20:03,514 --> 00:20:05,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's almost dawn.</b></font>

308
00:20:05,744 --> 00:20:08,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I guess we should head back, too.</b></font>

309
00:20:20,594 --> 00:20:23,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If I get serious, they can't keep up with me.</b></font>

310
00:20:23,134 --> 00:20:25,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They're still at that level...</b></font>

311
00:20:29,604 --> 00:20:31,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Finally caught up, huh?</b></font>

312
00:20:36,644 --> 00:20:37,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's not one of ours.</b></font>

313
00:20:37,944 --> 00:20:40,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Is that an MR2 or a 180?</b></font>

314
00:20:52,724 --> 00:20:55,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Nice driving. But after two corners,</b></font>

315
00:20:55,394 --> 00:20:57,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I won't even see you in my mirror.</b></font>

316
00:21:12,614 --> 00:21:14,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>An Eight-Six?!</b></font>

317
00:21:14,014 --> 00:21:15,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You've gotta be kidding!</b></font>

318
00:21:35,734 --> 00:21:39,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>My FD can't outrun an old Eight-Six?!</b></font>

319
00:21:39,704 --> 00:21:43,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Is this some sort of nightmare?! Crap!</b></font>

320
00:21:43,074 --> 00:21:46,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm the No. 2 driver of the Akagi Red Suns!</b></font>

321
00:21:51,424 --> 00:21:53,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Doesn't he know this road?</i></b></font>

322
00:21:53,424 --> 00:21:56,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>After this slow right, there's a sharp left.</i></b></font>

323
00:21:56,054 --> 00:21:58,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>If he doesn't slow down, he'll be in the ravine!</i></b></font>

324
00:22:01,334 --> 00:22:04,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I knew it! He's going too fast!</b></font>

325
00:22:04,594 --> 00:22:07,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There's no more room to slow down!</b></font>

326
00:22:12,744 --> 00:22:15,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What the hell?!</b></font>

327
00:22:16,844 --> 00:22:18,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Inertia drift?!</b></font>

328
00:22:43,774 --> 00:22:46,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>My pride says you gotta be wild and tough</i></b></font>

329
00:22:46,474 --> 00:22:48,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>So no one intervenes</i></b></font>

330
00:22:48,544 --> 00:22:50,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Never stop, I don't want to stop</i></b></font>

331
00:22:50,074 --> 00:22:52,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Even if you cry because of a sacrificed love</i></b></font>

332
00:22:52,144 --> 00:22:53,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Aim for the peak, sweep the winding street</i></b></font>

333
00:22:53,944 --> 00:22:56,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Beep beep! The warning chime is so cheap!</i></b></font>

334
00:22:56,154 --> 00:22:57,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The sheep should clear the road</i></b></font>

335
00:22:57,614 --> 00:23:00,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>'Cuz I'm never gonna stop, streak my dream</i></b></font>

336
00:23:00,054 --> 00:23:03,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Easy motivation is total stimulation</i></b></font>

337
00:23:03,924 --> 00:23:07,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>You tried to escape,</i>
<i>but anywhere is a safety zone</i></b></font>

338
00:23:07,994 --> 00:23:12,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Something is within your grasp</i>
<i>and something is forgotten</i></b></font>

339
00:23:12,004 --> 00:23:15,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Even if the world ends it will never change</i></b></font>

340
00:23:15,934 --> 00:23:24,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Beasty shout, no one can touch you</i></b></font>

341
00:23:24,014 --> 00:23:31,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Cross over now to the time of an intense dream</i></b></font>

342
00:23:31,384 --> 00:23:35,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Rage your dream, split the darkness</i></b></font>

343
00:23:35,424 --> 00:23:37,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Like a streak to the peak</i></b></font>

344
00:23:37,394 --> 00:23:43,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Erase the freezing darkness worldwide</i></b></font>

345
00:23:43,534 --> 00:23:47,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Rage your dream, and open the road</i></b></font>

346
00:23:47,404 --> 00:23:50,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Di-ding down, another round never slow down</i></b></font>

347
00:23:50,074 --> 00:23:52,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>A point 01 second knockdown</i></b></font>

348
00:23:52,074 --> 00:23:54,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Reverberations left behind,</i>
<i>disappear to the next town</i></b></font>

349
00:23:54,274 --> 00:23:56,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The losers are left in the dust</i></b></font>

350
00:23:56,114 --> 00:23:58,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Let's ignore the constraints of logic</i></b></font>

351
00:23:58,074 --> 00:24:00,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>'Cause they're a pain</i></b></font>

352
00:24:00,044 --> 00:24:02,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>A streaker runs naked across the street</i></b></font>

353
00:24:02,184 --> 00:24:03,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Something they would know</i></b></font>

354
00:24:03,384 --> 00:24:07,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Rage your dream,</i>
<i>continue on the unending road</i></b></font>

355
00:24:07,424 --> 00:24:11,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Don't look back on your love or your past</i></b></font>

356
00:24:11,424 --> 00:24:15,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Go forward and you'll shine brightly</i></b></font>

357
00:24:15,494 --> 00:24:20,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Rage your dream, you're living in the now</i></b></font>

358
00:24:26,204 --> 00:24:30,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Drift fans and Eight-Six owners!</i>
<i>Thanks for waiting!</i></b></font>

359
00:24:30,844 --> 00:24:32,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>At last it begins!</i></b></font>

360
00:24:32,414 --> 00:24:34,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Initial D!</i></b></font>

361
00:24:34,344 --> 00:24:35,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>What did you think of</i>
<i>Takumi's super drift technique,</i></b></font>

362
00:24:35,954 --> 00:24:39,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>racing his 1.6 liter non-turbo Eight-Six</i></b></font>

363
00:24:39,284 --> 00:24:42,024
