364
00:24:42,024 --> 00:24:44,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Pretty cool, don't you think?</i></b></font>

365
00:24:44,254 --> 00:24:46,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>And for those who understand</i>
